  "text": "Proof. Similar to the proof of [FWY18, Theorem 6.1], we prove Theorem 3.13 as follows. The first step is to consider the degeneration of X D,r to the normal cone and apply the degeneration formula to the cycle [M Γ (X D,r )] vir . The degeneration formula is simply the higher genus version of the degeneration formula in [CITATION_1] (15) ",
